<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zuó rì de zhōng xīn diū zài nǎ ér 迦南507</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zuó rì de zhōng xīn dōu shuō jiā cháng huà, zuó rì de zhōng xīn tóng hē yī wǎn chá,
 zuó rì de zhōng xīn tóng diǎn yī dēng yóu, zuó rì de zhōng xīn zěn me bù jiàn le,
 cí ài de jiù zhǔ xiàng wǒ men shuō huà, nǐ bǎ zhōng xīn diū zài nǎ ér,,
 chèn tiān de hái zài shén de cún liú xià, kuài bǎ zhōng xīn zhǎo huí lái ba,
 nǐ bǎ zhōng xīn diū zài nǎ ér, nǐ bǎ zhōng xīn diū zài nǎ ér,
 zhǔ jīn rì xiàng nǐ yào zhōng xīn, nǐ bǎ zhōng xīn diū zài nǎ ér.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>507</hymn_number>
</song>